CASE WHEN COALESCE(EFFECTIVE_DATE,'') <> '' AND EFFECTIVE_DATE <> '20691231' 
THEN to_date(TRIM(EFFECTIVE_DATE), 'yyyy-MM-dd') WHEN EFFECTIVE_DATE = '20691231' THEN to_date('9999-12-31',
'yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE to_date('1000-01-03','yyyy-MM-dd') END

CASE WHEN COALESCE(UPDATE_USER_DATE,"") <> "" AND UPDATE_USER_DATE <> "20691231" THEN to_date(TRIM(UPDATE_USER_DATE), "yyyyMMdd") WHEN UPDATE_USER_DATE = "20691231" THEN to_date("9999-12-31", "yyyy-MM-dd") ELSE to_date("1000-01-03","yyyy-MM-dd") END
